[SHORT DESC]
A Ball used to catch Pokemon that heals the caught Pokemon.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>A Ball used to catch Pokemon. Will fail during Trainer battles. Cannot be used in Link or Wi-Fi battles.</p>

<p>Has a capture modifier of *1. When caught in this Ball, the Pokemon has all of its HP restored and any status conditions removed.</p>